	<article class="post-19475 post type-post status-publish hentry tag-cowen-tyler tag-keynes-john-maynard tag-labor-and-jobs tag-longevity tag-murray-charles tag-productivity tag-working-hours per-cowen-tyler per-keynes-john-maynard per-murray-charles des-labor-and-jobs des-longevity des-productivity des-working-hours" id="post-19475">
